    "A selective search technique is utilized to choose potential boxes first, and then features are retrieved and predicted.",
    "When compared to the previous method, its accuracy is greatly enhanced, but there will be feature redundancy, which will slow down the network's performance.",
    "Fast RCNN 19 is an upgraded form of RCNN.",
    "It initially pulls features from the entire image, then uses ROI pooling and passes it to the fully connected layer to extract higher-level features, and lastly uses the Softmax layer to predict.",
    "This method eliminates the problem of recurrent feature extraction and significantly improves detection speed, but it still relies on the selective search algorithm to generate candidate regions, which has an impact on accuracy."
